										<span class="uael-accordion-icon-opened"><i class="fas fa-angle-up"></i></span>
									</span>
									<span class="uael-question-89063df uael-question-span" tabindex="0" id="uael-faq-4">What is the average profit margin for a restaurant?</span>
								</div>
								<div class="uael-accordion-content" role="tabpanel">
									<span>
									<span><p>The average profit margin for a restaurant is 7% (considering the net income).</p></span>									</span>
								</div>
							</div>
														<div id="uael-accordion-4d10504" class="uael-faq-accordion" role="tablist">
								<div class= "uael-accordion-title" aria-expanded="false" role="tab">
									<span class="uael-accordion-icon uael-accordion-icon-left">
